articles.author: Andrew van Leeuwen
articles.title: Fan injured in "freak one-off" Magnussen F1 debris incident at Australian GP - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Australian Grand Prix Corporation CEO Andrew Westacott has responded to what he says was a "freak, one-off" incident that saw a fan injured by debris on Sunday.
articles.content:
Westacott fronted media on Monday morning in Melbourne following what is his final race at the helm of the Australian GP promoter.
